    <h1 class="font-syne font-extrabold text-[#F1F0F7] leading-tight" style="font-size:clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px);">Guide Onboarding IT - Premier Jour | Nouvel arrivant</h1>
    <p class="text-[#9B99AA] text-sm mt-2 mb-0">Guide d</p>
